code: @Override public void apply(Collection<InstanceView<?>> data) {     if (consumer == null || data.isEmpty()) {         return.     }     if (sendItems) {         data.forEach(item -> consumer.sendMessage("Emitter", item)).     } else {         consumer.sendMessage("Emitter", data).     } }
@Override public EventCollection newCollection() {     return new BaseEventCollection(). }
